Package entity

Class CampInformation

Object
CampInformation
All Implemented Interfaces:
SerializeToCSV
public class CampInformation extends Object implements SerializeToCSV

This is a class to represent a camp. It stores information such as camp name, camp dates, total slots and more. Implemented using builder design pattern.

Since:
19-11-2023
Version:
1.0
Author:
Team 2
